<section id="To_change_settings_on_the_CloudForms_Management_Engine_Appliance" remap="TID_14893">
	<title>Changing Configuration Settings</title>
	<para>
		The procedure describes how to make changes to the configuration settings on the <productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> appliance.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Change Settings on the <productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> Appliance</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				After starting the appliance, log in with a user name of <literal>admin</literal> and the default password of <literal>smartvm</literal>. The <productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> Appliance summary screen displays.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Press <guibutton>Enter</guibutton> to manually configure settings.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Press the number for the item you want to change, and press <guibutton>Enter</guibutton>. The options for your selection are displayed.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Follow the prompts to make the changes.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Press <guibutton>Enter</guibutton> to accept a setting where applicable.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
	<note>
		<para>
			The <productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> Appliance console automatically logs out after five minutes of inactivity.
		</para>
	</note> 
